{"tid":382731,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺林保怡演技套套戲一樣","createTime":"2017-09-01T02:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T11:31:56.000Z","uid":81234,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cd828f5ad9ee61f760615cbd7758cdbb58051188","tid":382731,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"都係果個樣<br />\n唔明點樣拎視帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71ec3d01472fdc860e9df32ee2e5cfe9a895ec9","tid":382731,"uid":8717,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係果個樣<br />\n唔明點樣拎視帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然唔識駁你,但我就好鐘意睇佢拍劇,由十幾年前無線睇到近期綠豆<br />\n佢俾到我既感覺就係好真同埋反應好自然,唔做作,喊同笑都有一種好實在既感覺,而且十幾年後生果陣己經唔係太靚仔,即使劇中有感情線都會黎得實在,特別係綠豆入邊寫實既情節,令劇入邊既佢顯得似一個平凡人既生活寫照多於&quot;劇集主角&quot;.日日發生係你身邊咁"},{"pid":"ffbe07883cf5fcd4d687f613519390d8191003e2","tid":382731,"uid":101219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係果個樣<br />\n唔明點樣拎視帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印象最深係以前大時代結局，劉青雲贏左同林保怡攬住慶祝，林保怡個樣真係好開心好興奮，睇到我以為唔係拍戲係真係贏大錢<br />\n<br />\n依家大時代打颱風個gif都會見到"},{"pid":"7f9e6c2e220571caf2fc5785128e414258cd44df","tid":382731,"uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"一眼睇穿你"},{"pid":"e37a44e3857849f2b9212df8568e0700b17ee760","tid":382731,"uid":68033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"以前都可能係同一款咁 因為角色差唔多<br />\n都係有心事 好有計算咁<br />\n<br />\n但係綠豆完做柔情大衛真係上得神台<br />\n個賤婦走左之後自己喊<br />\n同埋對質 點解要我問你先講呀<br />\n<br />\n真係諗起都覺得犀利"},{"pid":"1f69f101e88a4af8f477c920b7045385efd7e085","tid":382731,"uid":44412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"天與地先係顛峰"},{"pid":"b3dfa054f49e4a576ec418c85997ece97edb6a16","tid":382731,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完讀心神探<br />\n覺得佢個樣永遠一樣<br />\n神槍手都係"},{"pid":"aa04946a9d3e7a09eb7f4577964444c984e06934","tid":382731,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:25:00.000Z","msg":"無睇過綠豆<br />\n同天興地鼓佬比較邊個演繹犀利D?"},{"pid":"f408d1d7a5d515f1792535b0078f1408a2e3bb8a","tid":382731,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:57:41.000Z","msg":"天與地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73509e8abfb55a25fc6b7499fe83c119d65d541b","tid":382731,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:58:44.000Z","msg":"唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa0fdd3a5fea4b6a7773bbb98ed16392b31bf5b","tid":382731,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"綠豆已經將以前無線啲底洗得一乾二淨"},{"pid":"c9afd8b59e5bdec4e668c8a2ed7b77539e8909f2","tid":382731,"uid":124450,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"佢係有搵食mode同認真mode<br />\n<br />\n讀心神探就搵食啦<br />\n同戚拍劇就真係睇到佢功力<br />\n<br />\n唔好講天與地<br />\n珠光寶氣度佢嘅表現已經好有質感<br />\n<br />\n講到尾<br />\n個角色有發揮空間佢一定交到成績<br />\n佢如果好似張家輝咁肯三幾四十歲搏一鋪係有能力拍到電影"},{"pid":"0472dd3744f0684d8af19e5cc696b39cb9bdb754","tid":382731,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"唔覺<br />\n我只覺得佢咁多年都好似無乜老過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109f42524fa5249a64e070612802aaebf4210e14","tid":382731,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:13:12.000Z","msg":"回家吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想睇佢返tvb拍劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d9cf0b1a49871855e92071d84d06e834782d51","tid":382731,"uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":